Magnus, Robot Fighter - Wikipedia






















 






Magnus, Robot Fighter

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Magnus, Robot Fighter



Magnus, Robot Fighter 4000 A.D. #1, Gold Key Comics



Publication information


Publisher
Gold Key Comics
Valiant Comics


