Product Description
Magnus Citrine has wandering vines and leaves in gray and yellow on a ivory background. This outdoor fabric from Robert Allen Home has a sophisticated look. First Quality Close Out and On Sale now for only $7.99 per yard limited quantity!
This printed polyester fabric is specified for outdoor occasional use only. Do not use in areas that require highly durable fabric specifications, such as indoor upholstery. It is best used for cushions or pillows that can be removed out of season.
